<plot>The story deals with the famous incident that occurred in schoolroom of Wrzesnia, near Prussian-Russian border of partitioned Poland, in 1901. The issue is the teaching of religion in German schools, a decision that draws a protest from Polish deputies in the German parliament. A local priest invoked the strike and continues to support the children when they refuse to participate in the lessons, even under beatings and threats.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?659389</url></doc>
